					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5763678#post-3775800</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5763678/scp-3761#post-3775800</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 21 Apr 2018 03:42:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Westrin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2858989</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Image&nbsp;stuff</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The factory image is Public Domain.</p> <p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Factory#/media/File:Air_pollution_by_industrial_chimneys.jpg">Source here</a>.</p> <p>The Scroll Image is by Giovanni Dall'Orto, under the following terms:</p> <blockquote> <p>The copyright holder of this file allows anyone to use it for any purpose, <strong>provided that the copyright holder is properly attributed.</strong> Redistribution, derivative work, commercial use, and all other use is permitted.</p> </blockquote> <p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Book#/media/File:2049_-_Byzantine_Museum,_Athens_-_Parchement_scroll,_13th_century_-_Photo_by_Giovanni_Dall%27Orto,_Nov_12.jpg">Source here</a>.</p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span>Where we once more can be with the Trees.</span></h2> </div> <hr /> <p>Huge, huge, huge thanks to everyone who looked at it while it was being worked on. Way too many people looked at it to name them all, but I appreciate every single one of you.</p> <p>Super special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/theesherm" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1583637&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1547621897" alt="TheeSherm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1583637)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/theesherm" >TheeSherm</a></span> for both looking at it, and giving me the courage to post it. Would not have done it without ya!</p> <p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Butler_County,_Kansas">Also here's Butler County's wikipedia page in case you were curious</a></p> <hr /> <h4><span>Art</span></h4> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">3761&nbsp;Polandball&nbsp;Fanart</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">By&nbsp;Phamtomguy</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/316354378640654336/418511681795129349/c3412c455655c3f5cd8d185490619f2a.png" alt="c3412c455655c3f5cd8d185490619f2a.png" class="image" /></div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">This&nbsp;counts&nbsp;I&nbsp;guess</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">by&nbsp;Numerophobie&nbsp;on&nbsp;Reddit</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://i.redd.it/g9gmjh2ami511.png" alt="g9gmjh2ami511.png" class="image" /></div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">An&nbsp;unfinished&nbsp;SCP-3761&nbsp;animation</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">By&nbsp;DrShine</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/316354378640654336/507417082212778014/image0.gif" alt="image0.gif" class="image" /> <p>More of their stuff can be found <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/drshine-art-page">here.</a></p> </div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A&nbsp;glorious&nbsp;Tree&nbsp;Critter&nbsp;portrait</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">by&nbsp;DrAnnoyingDog</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/r4S5CyE_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium" alt="r4S5CyE_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium" class="image" /></div> </div> </div> <hr /> 
				 	]]>
